item.title: 6th ATX Diversity Hackathon Rules and Judging criteria
item.description: There are the five following categories for prizes. All projects are eligible for all the categories. Deep learning - Sponsored by UI/UX - Sponsored by Social impact Technical stack Overall The max team size is 5 people. You can organize your own team. If you are looking for projects or teammates, please sign up for slack here and use the #pitch channel. Project presentation is on 9/20 (Sunday) 2:00 PM, central time.

item.title: 6th ATX Diversity Hackathon Workshop Schedule
item.description: FRIDAY = September 18 11:00 - 12:00 PM Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion can’t just be terms that we use at work Presenter: Briona Jenkins [twitter instagram] Visit Briona’s press page to listen to the panels and podcast, and the blog posts. 12:00 - 1:00 PM How to Not Die Broke: Investing Strategies You Need to Know Presenter: Kara Perez [twitter instagram] 2:00 PM Socket Programming in Python Presenter: Rachel Bentley [twitter]
